{"tid":2360912,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇 奧斯爾老友 愛華頓 杜信(Tosun)慶祝動作支持土耳其極端組織","createTime":"2021-01-10T07:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:11:28.000Z","uid":38189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a57a9f1e7d01cba95dcdce180aac6fc451048a98","tid":2360912,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVTEr7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVTEr7a.png&h=789941b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食指和小指豎起，做出了一個模仿狼頭的手勢。 而這是新法西斯右翼極端組織&ldquo;灰狼&rdquo;的標誌性手勢。<br />\n<br />\n 灰狼組織是位於土耳其的跨國超民族主義新法西斯組織，去年法國政府指責這個組織&ldquo;實施極端暴力行為，散佈極端暴力威脅，煽動對當局和亞美尼亞人的仇恨&rdquo;，並宣佈在法國禁止灰狼組織 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ma85nFQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fma85nFQ.png&h=70535add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土耳其=搞事狗 土耳其佬根本唔係反共 純粹想全世界都做伊斯蘭狗 奧斯爾支持厄爾多安都係仆街 達sir封殺無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614b5f9dbdfa85c100df314abfbab37949a15375","tid":2360912,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:56:44.000Z","msg":"Rock and roll 🤟🏼"},{"pid":"5e3deeb1255185fcac52fc764b21b4c90b65f7de","tid":2360912,"uid":91771,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://soranews24.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2013/06/babymetale383a1e382aee38384e3838d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoranews24.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2013%2F06%2Fbabymetale383a1e382aee38384e3838d.jpg&h=8f61386a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得babymetal比人話係邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a101787a60eb663de3b2